@LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5175

### 健康檢查
GET {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 設定 Line 參數與同步 Webhook Endpoint
POST {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/dashboard/api/line/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelAccessToken": "YOUR_CHANNEL_ACCESS_TOKEN",
  "channelSecret": "YOUR_CHANNEL_SECRET",
  "webhookUrl": "",
  "setEndpoint": true
}

###

### 取得 Bot 與 Webhook 資訊
GET {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/dashboard/api/line/info
Accept: application/json

###

### 取得最近 webhook 事件
GET {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/dashboard/api/line/events
Accept: application/json

###

### 測試 API webhook
POST {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/line/hook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: TODO

{
  "events": []
}

###

### 測試 Dashboard webhook
POST {{LineMessageApi.ExampleApi_HostAddress}}/dashboard/hook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: TODO

{
  "events": []
}
